# Copy to adb-wlan.conf and set your phone's wireless debugging address.
# Find it under: Developer options -> Wireless debugging -> IP address & port
#
# Examples:
#   192.168.1.42:5555
#   192.168.1.42:37845
#
# Android 11+ first-time pairing (run once in a terminal):
#   adb pair 192.168.1.42:37123
#   (enter the 6-digit code shown on the phone)
#   adb connect 192.168.1.42:5555
#
192.168.1.42:5555
